[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering constructor access**\n\nI'm thinking about whether a private nested class might be compiled as public and how that affects constructor access. It seems like the `getConstructors` method would only return public constructors, so a private constructor wouldn't show up. That's good to know! However, I can still instantiate the class from a companion method within the same object. It's an interesting concept, and I'm eager to explore it further!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0761881ea5089f5a016a40a6a5e3c48190ae87e1a1a85bd5b5\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQKa2HU7YxoHDgMfBSvfuB763-cQU8a4SM23Ei-rhmq_tyi_OZGNNhLIPDFLdtDpRhrpKcdAsFj_zS0A6pv-s2u0lCmtETdgaP-foMSaUPLzghFZ4o_WQwjrjk8WddXTvegWBphRCFk_q-VUSSGN5uYRRiBUtJ3t8oCqohFjYBEla2Z-Da8isetX-qB-RE3UEC1ttJ66LxyC2gkyMcHEghBhplC7HB6TvcYJ9iN6UoO9jbf1ZTjP2dCYQZw_8YridX7YDt_lSIFYvR5WqEL-oKalxvcz9K3dgy9wln9lP2XtFDE1x542QngDS7Swu6s_xQlXnUgwOobiL1Rmt_EzPSLXcrZoX5hQ9JVK9V0cXpNFr3qPcfn_c3O421oSAvfWUz4R2ZqfT_Mjg1bfVYwmLhdmXB7EJELygVVM2xX8M3cceqZwtKYwpPNYfaOG9XbloA_4P-M_-Ko2Fp6FyYWg8Q6-7dCWhforwgDYl6yqxm5xPmyuv6yodnkX5ZCtIKVbklQ1uaye2oNcN_WV8TNs6TMAzUVeQyzzSGQtx6ZL6ak5ZSme5iFq72ZYwIWqCNhXKCynrQjn2kIpLMjyv3f-q-oSJ31l72mvhu5hdFPhWoBuEsMpmQJVswx62GNAfFS8cj14m3sCyivsUgQsjhFFGBSABys1-TIm8Bo5e-u_7AHoCQySuSX1zZ6zXGPXiN-6mEiEvjMxRA-rryE9HphIiRoO1LOSS1HgQDJ1gCF8NVVOabi2Y5H3BXES70gM-uHNRkeAUPWcugR2GUO8ZLXVFH6JFDIM8TRIiBBPZ5kFWThBVc4USZlTpQ5yI6bxrgVYKBRJmTVKsNMnOR1Y_j3URn_ElEgTg_4uocQSzyS6ivYV6_MG6tQe6aumd8Uh35hl4GG1W9pie1dVc1Wi4rvBs_xxbaqffQDkbERgZbnjTECkJGSu3JODtNKa5IZA16Guiq7oUGhKe89TbT34PcOjXJbdNQQGPwnr7F5Fq8CHDjSNkGHQebMEf-AlQcSp6LiMxDvGn90jXmSU5MToqMQ2KrmoKbbLdcBuPmcTyAwqczhyPqp4y6QIGsS0UipHYmrNW57ur_bGKMyeTCE8gUPFr6vTUpbpvHQSZMdJzFf1TFHUun8Qk_nhbuWOhbqUbiCeeHL-pKCSB-E_dIsntJX08cTI9PR1tfkY1hPITFkBWwERmlp-MOQsdfWXMStvM7dO92dioLZmdgLnm1kXf5u7LQu1EcYiMv6lVRQTXiXQV0GZ_ccwjJq6-eoBTq